Le climat, les hommes et la mer

Travel Documentary hosted by Georges Pernoud, published by TV5Monde broadcasted as part of TV5Monde Thalassa series in 2015 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/6/6b/Le-climat-les-hommes-et-la-mer-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

Climate, people and the sea.
Victor lives in Paita, Peru. This coastal village owes its prosperity to the fishing of pota, a giant squid. The Pacific waters are teeming with fish in this region where upwelling caused by the Humboldt Current brings nutrients up from the depths. But like elsewhere, things are changing.
